legacy.description: Permanent Representative of the People's Republic of China to the United Nations. See also https://t.co/gGUiTCoPqT
legacy.name: Zhang Jun

result.text: The Council has so far held several meetings on the Palestinian-Israeli Situation. It cannot be said that there was no consensus at all. The resolution just adopted by the General Assembly has also pointed the Council in the right direction. In the face of the current critical situation, China once again solemnly calls on the Council to strengthen unity, build consensus, and take responsible and meaningful actions as soon as possible. We believe that so long as we focus on the most pressing issues such as a ceasefire and an end to the fighting, the protection of civilians, and the prevention of a larger humanitarian disaster, it is possible for members of this Council to reach consensus, and indeed this is what we should do. At this juncture. silence means acquiescence, and inaction is tantamount to a green light. The eyes of the world are upon us, and history will record our choice.

result.text:
The past decade of 🇨🇳#China’s international development cooperation and foreign aid.

➡️Humanitarian relief: ⭐ $1 million in cash assistance + 15 million yuan ($2.06 million) in emergency humanitarian supplies to the Gaza Strip ⭐ 1,000+ cases of emergency assistance to 70+ countries ⭐ emergency food aid to 30+ countries since 2022. 

➡️Against COVID-19 pandemic: ⭐ materials to 153 countries and 15 int’l organizations ⭐ medical expert groups to 34 countries ⭐ 2.3+ bln doses of vaccines to 110+ countries and 4 int’l organizations. 

➡️Construction of BRI: ⭐ 2,000+ assistance projects arranged with 120+ BRI partner countries ⭐ 80+ economic & trade cooperation zones established, mobilizing nearly $1 tln in investment ⭐ 100,000+ experts trained & nearly 40 mln people lifted out of poverty.

➡️Implementation of GDI: ⭐ 200+ "small but beautiful" projects in 60+ countries.

➡️Bilateral and tripartite cooperation: ⭐ cooperation with 20+ int’l organizations, deploying 130+ projects in nearly 60 countries, which benefited 30+ mln people.

FM Wang also held two rounds of talks with @SecBlinken, and conducted strategic communication with NSA @JakeSullivan46.
